#{{countable}} The [[organ]] of [[hearing]], consisting of the [[pinna]], [[auditory canal]], [[eardrum]], [[malleus]], [[incus]], [[stapes]] and [[cochlea]].
#{{countable}} {{slang}} A [[police]] [[informant]]. 
